Type: Package
Package: printtree
Title: Print Directory Trees for R Projects and Folders
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Arthur", , "prigasgenthian48@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Prints a compact directory tree for a specified folder.
    Optionally detects RStudio project files and can print from the
    project root. Designed for quick inspection of project structure from
    the console.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/PrigasG/printtree
